name: Coffee Lab
longDescription: Coffee lab has good coffee and a lot of warm and cold drink options. My only problem with it is that it is not consistent. Sometimes the drinks are really good and other times it just gets messed up. Their iced coffee though is really good. The baked goods are not always fresh unfortunately, but when they are, they are really good and well done. Prices are within Ramallah’s average..

name: Sufi Cafe
longDescription: Incredibly nice atmosphere, very caring staff, good coffee, cold drinks and sweets even hookahs. It's a bit outside the busy centre of Ramallah and perfect for a break or to sit and study. An experience no one should miss when visiting, menus are also available in English and you can ask for everything! Just as pretty in real life as in the pictures..

name: Cafe Antique
description: good choice for cafe if you want to get your kids with you .
longDescription: such a nice and simple place to spend time in it  . you feel like home there between in these old rooms  you can also find out the old town of nablus through this palce  also the owner of the place is such a great person  friendly and kind and will let you feel like he knew you from ages  with all of his knowledge  and experience he will be a great guide  and friend  , add to that near Antiuque cafe you will find a related place called teriquaze  which is ownd by the same owner  of Antique  its a hostel and a cafe at the same time   .  to be honest Antique is so simple  thats why i do recommend it 🌸..

name: مطعم التيتي
description: Best option for trying ventage place  .

name: Vintage Cafe
description: Best option for trying ventage place.
longDescription: The food here was fantastic. We ordered sushi mostly and some salads. The restaurant is in a great location too, but the service was super bad. The servers were just unwelcoming. Only reason i gave it 4 stars is because of the service. Spectacular food otherwise! Definitely recommend giving it a try for tourists..

name: Kunnache Cafe
description: Best option for trying luxury place  .

Seating Options: Indoor seating for a cozy atmosphere and outdoor seating for scenic views.Customer Service: Renowned for friendly and attentive staff who ensure a pleasant experience. Special Events: Often hosts live music nights, private events, and themed evenings.
